<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/26792268-fear-city"><img alt="Fear City: New York&#39;s Fiscal Crisis and the Rise of Austerity Politics" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1482832457l/26792268._SX98_.jpg" />
