          <a href="/book/show/1308640.Whose_Detroit_"><img id="more_book_1308640" alt="Whose Detroit?: Politics, Labor, and Race in a Modern American City" title="Whose Detroit?: Politics, Labor, and Race in a Modern American City" width="50" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348931547l/1308640._SX98_.jpg" /></a>
